Package: mountainlab
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, nodejs
Description: Data processing, sharing and visualization software for scientists.
 The software comprises tools for processing electrophysiological recordings and for visualizing and validating the results.

Package: mountainlab-mpdock
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, nodejs, docker.io
Recommends: octave
Description: mpdock is a tool for mountainlab.
 The mpdock tool allows one to run mountainlab processors in docker containers.

